import { StyleSheet } from 'react-native';

const HomeStyle = StyleSheet.create({
  Iphone_11_Pro_Max: {
    width: 414,
    height: 896,
    display: 'flex',
    flexDirection: 'column',
    alignItems: 'center',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    background: 'radial-gradient(50% 39.96% at 0% 0%, rgba(71, 249, 249, 0.2) 0%, rgba(95, 200, 243, 0) 100%), radial-gradient(81.28% 61.44% at -14.49% 68.97%, #38a6f4 0%, rgba(168, 185, 247, 0) 100%), radial-gradient(173.31% 73.19% at 96.62% 58.59%, #eab9e6 1.56%, #e8abf8 32.55%, rgba(72, 207, 244, 0) 100%), #48cff4',
    borderRadius: 30,
  },
  topinfo: {
    background: 'none',
    borderRadius: 30,
    width: 414,
    height: 896,
    display: 'flex',
    flexDirection: 'column',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  Khung: {
    background: '#fff',
    borderRadius: 30,
    width: 300,
    height: 100,
    display: 'flex',
    flexDirection: 'row',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  h1: {
    display: 'flex',
    alignItems: 'flex-end',
    color: '#6495ED',
  },
  buttonmenu: {
    width: 414,
    height: 414,
    display: 'flex',
    borderRadius: 30,
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
    flexDirection: 'column',
  },
  option: {
    width: 414,
    height: 100,
    display: 'flex',
    alignItems: 'center',
    flexDirection: 'row',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    padding: 10,
    gap: 44,
  },
  rectangle: {
    width: 100,
    height: 100,
    background: '#71ddff',
    padding: 30,
    fontSize: 45,
    borderWidth: 0,
    borderRadius: 100,
    cursor: 'pointer',
    color: 'rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4)',
  },
});

export default HomeStyle;
